properties.name: text
properties.value:
Group Chairman

Mr. Murali Krishna, an entrepreneur with an overall business experience of more than 30 years is the chairman of the company. He has more than 20 years of realty experience in Bangalore and Hyderabad, and has undertaken mixed developments like residential, commercial and retail. Apart from real estate, his vast experience also spans other industries such as food processing and manufacturing. He spearheads the design and engineering team and is the key driving force for timely and quality delivery.

properties.name: text
properties.value:
Managing Director – Mr. Venu Vinod

Mr. Venu Vinod is an established entrepreneur from Hyderabad. He started his business career in the year 1982 and has been exposed to diverse business verticals such as trading in engineering products, chemicals and construction equipment. He comes with a vast experience spanning more than 20 years’ worth of real estate activities in Hyderabad, undertaking development of commercial and industrial projects in and around the city. He is one of the promoters of Cybercity, and is the Managing Director, looking after the daily operations and providing guidance to the staff.

properties.name: text
properties.value:
Executive Director – Mr. K. Vijaya Bhaskar Reddy

Mr. Vijaya Bhaskar Reddy is one of the promoters of Ashoka Builders and Cybercity Builders, two of the renowned brands in the Hyderabad real estate market. He brings with him years of rich experience in real estate, especially in handling mega projects and integrated developments. Under his stewardship as Executive Director, Cybercity has, over the years, carved a niche for itself.

properties.name: text
properties.value:
Director – Mrs. K. Maheshwari

Mrs. Maheshwari is an entrepreneur and also the promoter of M/s. Venkatalakshmy Foods Pvt. Ltd., a decade old company operating in agri yield trading. Its clientele includes renowned brands such as Pepsi Co. Currently, she is a director in Cybercity. She contributes to the strategic decision-making of the board.

properties.name: text
properties.value:
Director – Mr. Srivardhan Reddy

Mr. Srivardhan is a graduate in business management with experience in manufacturing and trading. Today, he heads the daily operations and execution of the construction activities at various Cybercity projects in his capacity as a director.
